character_name: Alice and her clones; former Umbrella Corporation security officer turned rogue fighter
Claire Redfield; One of Alice's former allies
Chris Redfield; United States military elite soldier and the older brother of Claire
Albert Wesker; the Chairman of the Umbrella Corporation who possesses superhuman strength
Luther West; a former professional basketball player who leads the band of the survivors of Los Angeles.
Bennett Sinclair; a former film producer and one of the survivors of Los Angeles.
Crystal Waters; a junior champion in swimming in her high school days
Kim Yong; Bennett's former intern before the virus outbreak and also one of the survivors.
K-Mart; a young girl named after the department store where she was discovered hiding
Jill Valentine; former S.T.A.R.S. member & police officer of Raccoon City who helped Alice escape after the city's destruction incident
